{"tid":181180,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【一齊同女神傾偈】我膽粗粗約女神談善言傾偈，佢竟然應承左！","createTime":"2017-03-31T12:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T22:44:35.000Z","uid":37653,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78acc38867713709cb5a4defbb2f22c5342807bd","tid":181180,"uid":37653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>談善言<br />\n榮獲提名第36屆香港電影金像獎【最佳新演員】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/e43ff1302a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fe43ff1302a.jpg&h=589e75e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/e43feda69f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fe43feda69f.jpg&h=e4d0b756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/e43fc630b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fe43fc630b2.jpg&h=98d29a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/e44092752e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fe44092752e.jpg&h=97887c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我三個月前開始，每日迫自己搵一位陌生人傾偈<br />\n然後將對話內容打成一篇篇嘅文章，放上Facebook Page<br />\n我遇過 馬匹訓練員、精神病人、香港小姐、英國領事 等等<br />\n<br />\n我之前喺創意台開嘅POST：<br />\n【練膽大法】我每日迫自己搵一位陌生人傾偈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/153503/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/153503/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n搵人傾「陌樂偈」令小弟改變咗好多<br />\n大膽咗，有自信咗，想做乜就即刻去做<br />\n<br />\n最近，除咗同陌生人傾偈<br />\n我決定試下搵識得嘅人傾偈<br />\n因為識得嘅人，比陌生人更加重要，更加值得傾<br />\n<br />\n適逢《香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮》即將舉行<br />\n我嘗試邀請同金像獎有關嘅電影人，直播同大家一齊傾偈<br />\n<br />\n由於小弟係《點五步》嘅剪接，有幸同談善言見過幾次面<br />\n於是我膽粗粗問佢可唔可以同我一齊直播傾偈<br />\n結果佢經理人竟然答應咗！約咗我今晚去佢公司傾偈！<br />\n<br />\n直播會喺今晚10:30開始！<br />\n談善言除咗同小弟傾偈，亦會同各位巴打傾偈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>直播網址：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChatToStranger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChatToStranger&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8457c309\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChatToStranger</a>"},{"pid":"0603ec79f1f2cf907f78947cf2492f286e925238","tid":181180,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26710a10114f82a17a3ca8c0d95ac7e00569ee76","tid":181180,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858e6b748fd1fce17c5f3bb5f91871b536d06c14","tid":181180,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"原來你係點五步既crew，之前有睇陌樂偈個post，寫得好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4440688b1c1f60f09d01894074ddb6a64da1542b","tid":181180,"uid":37653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來你係點五步既crew，之前有睇陌樂偈個post，寫得好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb21590eeb5c7415066b5561cce8d3ff31cf248","tid":181180,"uid":37653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我怕一陣緊張到出唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab00cd896b5863dda961114e2c6aabc99a69512","tid":181180,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"一直有追巴打個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d309141e6424328be0ef24c9a5d078045499bd","tid":181180,"uid